description:
This is a market on whether doland tremp (https://twitter.com/dolandtremp_sol) or im boden (https://twitter.com/bodenonsolana) will have the most liked post made on March 7.

This market will resolve to "$tremp" if @dolandtremp_sol has the most liked post on March 7. 
This market will resolve to "$boden" if @bodenonsolana has the most liked post on March 7.
This market will resolve to 50-50 if they are tied (for example if both Tremp's and Boden's most liked post shows 2.1k likes, this market will resolve to 50-50).

For the purposes of resolving this market, only main feed posts (including quote posts) will count. Replies and reposts will NOT count for this market's resolution, in addition to posts deleted before March 8, 2024, 12:00 AM ET. 

The resolution for this market will be based on checking the most liked post made by each account between March 7, 2024, 12:00 AM ET (inclusive) and March 7, 2024 11:59 PM ET (inclusive) at precisely March 8, 2024, 12:00 AM ET. If upon check at resolution time, one of the accounts has no posts on March 7 or was banned/deleted, this market will resolve to the other account. If both have no posts/were banned/deleted, this market resolves 50-50.

Likes will be determined based on their appearance on X's desktop interface in English ET, as shown at the time of assessment, including any rounding shown. More granular numbers using different languages/regions will NOT be considered.
